</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_593" id="295v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_593_r2l17">Gemeiner Reychs . Stette potten 
<del rend="strikethrough">als </del> der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l19">
<del rend="strikethrough">Vlm dy <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> cʒu </del> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>aynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_593_r2l18">in <expan>Swab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> als dy <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> cʒu vlm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l20">beyeinander geweſen ſein etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l21"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Ewren brief vns bey dem gegenvvertigen
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l22">poten geſant / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol
                        vernomen / Vnd wöllen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l23">ſölch ewr <expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> den Steten
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nachgepawren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l24">in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> teıl gern alſo
                        verkünden . Auch iſt vns von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l25"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincʒ wegen in ſunderheit bıʒ her </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l26">kein <expan>anmutu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>beſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . vvol het der Edell her
                                <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l27"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> cʒu pickembach
                                <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincʒ Rate </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l28">nach <expan>etliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Rats geſant mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Er auſʒ <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l29"><expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geredt hat . Vnd het
                        dauon gern ein antwurtt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l30">gehabt / Aber dıe ward Jm von
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> abgeſlagen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l32">
<add><ab facs="#facs_593_r1l1">Alſo </ab></add> daʒ ſich der vnſer <add><ab facs="#facs_593_r2l31">darauff </ab></add> keiner antvvurtt <del rend="strikethrough">darauff ʒ </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l33">verfieng <del rend="strikethrough">darauff </del>
                        ʒetun . Vnd wo etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l34"><expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> Mathie
                                <expan>Ap<ex>oſto</ex>lı</expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_593" id="295v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Gemeiner reychs stette potten der <expan>v<ex>er</ex>aynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<add>in <expan>Swab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>, als dy
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> czu Ulm beyeinander gewesen sein
                        etc. </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, ewren brief, uns bey dem gegenwertigen
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> poten gesant,
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol vernomen und wöllen sölch ewr
                                <expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> den steten,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nachgepawren, in
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> teil gern also verkünden. Auch ist uns
                        von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincz wegen in sunderheit bizher kein
                                <expan>anmutu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>bescheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Wol het der edell her
                                <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> czu
                        Pickembach, <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincz rate, nach
                                <expan>etliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> rats gesant, mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        er ausz <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geredt hat, und het davon gern ein antwurtt
                        gehabt, aber die ward im von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> abgeslagen, <add>also</add> daz sich der
                        unser <add>darauff</add> keiner antwurtt verfieng ze tun. Und wo etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                            <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Mathie
                            <expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
